  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink254-kilavi">uṭaṉpōkk uṭaṉpaṭa vēṇṭiya tōḻi talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.   </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">
          What the confidante, who desired that [they] agree to elopement, told the heroine.
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink254">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟava ṉāra maṟutteṉa</l>
<l>naṟumpukai cūḻntu kānta ṇāṟum</l>
<l>vaṇṭimir cuṭarnutaṟ kuṟumakaḷ</l>
<l>koṇṭaṉar celvartaṅ kuṉṟukeḻu nāṭṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">

        <l>O young woman with the bright forehead where bees hum,</l>
        <l>he will take you and go to the hill country</l>
        <l>fragrant with Malabar glory lilies,</l>
        <l>surrounded by fragrant smoke,</l>
        <l>as the hill-dweller cuts the sandalwood tree.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
